name: iOS Apps by David Young
body:
### Support for my iOS apps

If you are having a problem with any of the apps I created, feel free to send my an email at david [at sign] deepinthecode.com.  Please put the name of the app in the Subject field after the word "Support:".  Thank you!

David Young
[deepinthecode.com](http://deepinthecode.com)
